OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMainly dry
OL,6,Fthis evening with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,8,Flargely dry and cloudy, a little rain
OL,9,Fpossible across the far west later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAfter a cloudy start it will
OL,12,Fbe a dry day with plenty of sunshine
OL,13,Fdeveloping by afternoon. Warm.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,16,FOutbreaks of rain spreading east on
OL,17,FSaturday, heavy at times. Scattered
OL,18,Fshowers on Sunday. Further rain likely
OL,19,Fon Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
